body.name: SODAY Pots and Pans Set Non Stick, 12 Pcs Kitchen Cookware Sets Induction Cookware Granite Cooking Set with Frying Pans, Saucepans, Steamer Silicone Shovel Spoon & Tongs (White)
features: Superior Granite Quality: Feature premium granite coating ensures long-lasting durability and exceptional non-stick properties, making cooking a breeze. Non-toxic cookware sets allow you to cook healthy and safe.
Rapid & Even Heat: Nonstick pots and pans set is equipped with durable aluminum core to make pan sets heats up quickly and distributes heat evenly, ensuring efficient and precise culinary results.
Compatible with All Stovetops: From gas to electric and induction, nonstick cookware set are designed to work flawlessly on any cooktop.

Durable Bakelite Handle: With heat-resistant properties allow you do not worry about burning fingers in picking up the pots and pans. Perspective glass lid ergonomic design allow you to check the status of the food in the pot in time.

Versatile Cooking Set: SODAY 12 pcs kitchen cookware set includes 9 inch/11 inch frying pans, 11 inch/4.5QT saute pan with lid,4.3 QT saucepan with lid and steamer,1.5 QT saucepan with lid and silicone shovel spoon & tongs ideal for your daily cooking.

Reliable After-sale Guarantee：If you have received defective nonstick pots and pans set due to delivery, please do not hesitate to contact us, You will be guaranteed a full refund or a new replacement.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful, durable non-stick cookware at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: I fell in love with this pots and pans set because of the beautiful white granite and the wood-look of the handles! I'm even more pleased now that I've had a chance to cook with them - they are 100% non-stick! I use a gas stove and have had no problems with even heat distribution, and cleanup is very easy (no elbow grease required!). Such a great price for such a classy, durable, high-performance product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great deal on pots and pans
reviews.reviewText: I love the color and they are non stick. They cook evenly which is also a plus. Easy to clean and doesn’t stain since they are white. Love the wooden handles. Great price. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely amazing pots and pans set!!
reviews.reviewText: The non stick is great! I have a gas stove so it’s hard to find a good nonstick pots and pan set that works. So far everything I’ve cooked wipes right off after which makes for such an easy clean. They heat up evenly and look amazing! I love this set and definitely highly recommend!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: This set has everything you need and looks nice to boot. Durable and easy to clean. Value exceeds cost in my opinion. Works well with my gas stove.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and functional
reviews.reviewText: These pans work really well and clean nicely. I was worried about stains because they are white but that has not been an issue! They heat up quickly and cook evenly. Great deal for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great pots and pans set
reviews.reviewText: Love these pots and pans they are very pretty and have a highly non stick surface. they are made well, only one thing I didn’t like was one of the pans seemed like the handle wobbled ever so slightly I tightened the screw but it still felt the same way. so not sure if it’s supposed to do that or what but still am very pleased with them. I personally just wash them by hand because there so easy to wash and nothing sticks to them the food just risnses off easily. Great purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice pans- if you cook a lot might not be for you.
reviews.reviewText: They're nice pans but I cook a lot and one of the pans is already peeling on the bottom, it's like the bottom burned off from too much usage and I've had them less than 2 months. Again I think they're good for the price, but I cook a lot so maybe not for someone that will use them most days.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exceptional Performance and Durability
reviews.reviewText: I recently upgraded my kitchen with the SODAY 12-Piece Non-Stick Cookware Set and it's been a fantastic experience. This set, with its superior non-stick surface, ensures hassle-free cooking and cleaning. Each piece offers even heat distribution, preventing hot spots and ensuring consistent cooking. The durability is impressive, showing no wear despite daily use. The variety in pot and pan sizes caters to all my cooking needs, and the ergonomic handles make handling a breeze. Additionally, their dishwasher-safe feature makes clean-up effortless. Overall, this cookware set has significantly enhanced my cooking routine with its quality, versatility, and convenience. Highly recommended for any kitchen enthusiast!
